Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Opalescence. Can you just picture it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Moi, stepping up in astounding new gown\Nat the Grand Galloping Gala in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yes! I did make it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Opal, of course you can help me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? You wanna help me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, aren't you the sweetest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful now. Don't move.\NThis shouldn't take long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh... Can't you see Rarity\Nis trying to concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think she's makin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes sense.\NSince this is a dressmaker's shop and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so very sorry to trouble you,\NRarity, but I need a quick favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please fix the button for me?\NIt's my dress for the Grand Galloping Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no! You can't wear this... old thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a glamorous new outfit for the Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll make it for you. No problem at all.\NIt will be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's really sweet of you to offer,\NRarity, but I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be so much work. This dress is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle.\NI insist on making you a new dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-No no, not a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case... Thank you\Nfor your generosity, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing your handiwork, I'm sure\Nit will be absolutely beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, Applejack.\NYou don't want a new gown either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gown? Shoot. I was just gonna\Nwear my old work duds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly be serious, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely must wear formal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I just spruce up your...\Nduds for you a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure. Why not?\NSince you're up for it and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't make them too... froufrou-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out below!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. New trick. Didn't quite work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you an outfit for\Nthe Gala too, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Outfit for the what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make one for you and you and all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And of course Pinkie and Fluttershy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and when I'm done, we can\Nhold our very own fashion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great idea!\NIf you're sure you can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it'll be a little bit of work, but it\Nwill be a wonderful boost for my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I love fun things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.\NWe'll have a fashion show starring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you have to do is make a\Ndifferent, stunnin', original...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...amazin' outfit for one, two, three, four,\Nfive... plus yourself, six ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And lickety split?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound as if it's going to be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thread by thread, stitching it together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twilight's dress\NCutting out the pattern snip by snip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making sure the fabric folds nicely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the perfect color and so hip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always gotta keep in mind my pacing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making sure the cloth's correctly facing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm stitching Twilight's dress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yard by yard, fussing on the details{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jewel neckline\NDon't you know a stitch in time saves nine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make her something perfect to inspire{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though she hates formal attire{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotta mind those intimate details{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though she's more concerned with sales{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Applejack's new dress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dressmaking's easy\NFor Pinkie Pie something pink{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy something breezy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blend color and form...{\i0}\NDo you think it looks cheesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something brash, perhaps quite fetching{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hook and eye\NCouldn't you just simply die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making sure it fits forelock and crest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget some magic in the dress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though it rides high on the flank{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rainbow won't look like a tank{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm stitching Rainbow's dress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Piece by piece, snip by snip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Croup, dock, haunch, shoulders, hip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thread by thread, primmed and pressed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yard by yard, never stressed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's the Art of the Dress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Keep them closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can look now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your new outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of your old duds now,\NApplejack? Pretty swanky, are they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Twilight! I made this dress for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I designed each outfit theme to perfectly\Nreflect each pony's unique personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it took me forever to get the colors right\Non this one, Rainbow Dash, but I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and it turned out\NBEAUTIFUL, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo, and I know you are going to love\Nyours, Fluttershy. It just sings spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Pinkie Pie, look! Pink! Your favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they all amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're...\N-Yeah, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-...sumth'n.\N-Yes! Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love something! Something is my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's the matter? Don't you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're plum grateful, cause\Nyou worked so hard on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's just not as cool as I was imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what we're all saying is that\Nthey're just not what we had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty more where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They were only a first pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my friends and I want\Nyou to be 110% satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry, I'll redo them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity. You don't have to do that.\NThey're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to be better that just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to think they're absolutely perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\NI mean, we wouldn't wanna impose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's no imposition. Really, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case... Thank you again, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I gotten myself into?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see me, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Your new-new gown's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely revised it and\NI know you're going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you should just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or love it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... both?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop asking me this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just tell me what you really think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, tell me, tellmetellmetellme!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Since you really wanna know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The armscye's tight, the middy collar\Ndoesn't go with the shawl lapel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...the hems are clearly machine-stitched,\Nthe pleats are uneven, the fabric looks like toile...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...you used a backstitch here when it clearly called for a\Ntopstitch or maybe a traditional blanket stitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the overdesign is reminiscent of\Nprêt-à-porter and not true French haute couture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh... you know...\Num, whatever you want to do is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the stars on my belt need\Nto be technically accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Orion has three stars on his belt, not four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stitch by stitch, stitching it together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deadline looms\NDon't know the client's always right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my fabric choice was perfect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got to get them all done by tonight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pinkie Pie, the color's too obtrusive{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait until you see it in the light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sewing them together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think my gown would be\Nmore "me" with some lollipops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, I think...\N-Balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well...\N-DO EET!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hour by hour, one more change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sewing them together, take great pains{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy, you're putting me in a bind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rainbow Dash, what is on your mind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my gosh, there's simply not much time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget, Applejack's duds must shine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dressmaking's easy\NEvery customer's call{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brings a whole new revision{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have to pick up the pace\NStill hold to my vision{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That constellation is Canis Major, not Minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,French haute couture, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it rains? Galoshes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,More balloons! Oh no, that's too many balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,More candy! Oh, less candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, I know. Streamers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Streamers?\N-Whose dress is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Streamers it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to tell me\Nto change something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just want my dress to be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not like the color?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The color's fine, just make it look cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not like the shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape's fine, just make\Nthe whole thing... you know, cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be about 20% cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All we ever want is indecision{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All we really like is what we know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotta balance style with adherence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making sure we make a good appearance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you simply have to fudge it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make sure that it stays within our budget{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got to overcome intimidation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember, it's all in the presentation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Piece by piece, snip by snip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Croup, dock, haunch, shoulders, hip{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bolt by bolt, primmed and pressed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yard by yard, always stressed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's the Art of the Dress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Opal. These are the ugliest\Ndresses I've ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I did exactly what each of you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know what you really think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh my!\N-It's... perfect!\N-It's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. They're the best duds I ever did see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly what I asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you as happy with the as we're?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm... happy that all of you are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just relieved to finally be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are never gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of Hoity-Toity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigwig fashion hotshot in Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. He heard about your fashion show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I happened to mention it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming here all the way from\NCanterlot to see your work, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Nelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You could sell a ton o' dresses to this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You business will be boomin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoity-Toity?\NHe's coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To see THESE dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Get ready for all\Nof your dreams to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Relax, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends like their outfits and so will he.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the lights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. That means the show's starting. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the beginning of time the elite\Nof Equestria have longed for pony fashions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...that that truly expressed the\Nessence of their very souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Patiently waiting decades... no, centuries!\N...for the perfect pony gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at long last, Equestria, your wait is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for the breathtaking\Ndesigns of Ponyville's own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everypony lookin' at us like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we overdid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those amateurish designs look like a piled-on\Nmishmash of everything but a kitchen sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a travesty, it's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those outfits are the ugliest things\NI've ever seen, oh for shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is responsible for subjecting\Nour eyes to these horrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention wasting my valuable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out and take a bow, Rarity.\NYou worked really hard for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Alright, woohoo! Go, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity? You okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't come out for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never coming out! I can't\Nshow my face in Ponyville ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be somepony. I used to be respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I made dresses. Beautiful, beautiful dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But now everypony is laughing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing but a laughingstock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a laughingstock, Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-She kind of is.\N-Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out and talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I vant to be alone! I want to wallow in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...whatever it is that ponies\Nare supposed to wallow in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ponies wallow in pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, listen to me, I don't even know\Nwhat I'm supposed to wallow in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M SO PATHETIC!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Panic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your answer for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't just leave Rarity like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll become a crazy cat lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She only has one cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Exile...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess technically I'd have to\Nmove away to live in exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would I go? And what would I pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's going to take me forever\Nto do all of that packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to pack\Nwhen you go into exile?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you supposed to pack warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Opal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Opal, how did you get up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, you poor dear! Mama's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you strand my poor Opal on the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how else were we gonna get\Nyou out here to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? It's not... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We all finished your dress for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Fluttershy's\Nfreaky knowledge of sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh. She doesn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I LOVE IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You ponies did an amazing job.\NIt's exactly the way I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We just followed your brilliant design.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we should have let you do for our outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those first dressed you designed were perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so super sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You worked really hard to make our\Ndresses exactly the way we wanted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We all saw how well that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's mighty big of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But my whole career is still ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. That.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I haven't got all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this can't be the same designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly I have a fresh craving\Nfor some Dutch apple pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Candied apples on a stick?\NApple turnovers? Apple cobbler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is a fashion show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these dresses are absolutely amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is responsible?\NStep forward, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnifico! Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"This week my very talented\Nfriend Rarity learned..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"...that if you try to please everypony,\Nyou oftentimes end up pleasing nopony."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Especially yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"And I learned this:"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"When somepony offers to do you a favor..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"...like making you a beautiful dress..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"...you shouldn't be overly critical\Nof something generously given to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"In other words, you shouldn't\Nlook a gift horse in the mouth."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, my congratulations.\NYou are the most impressive fashion maven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you do me the great honor\Nof allowing me to feature your couture...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...in my best of the best boutique in Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll need you to make a dozen\Nof each dress for me by next Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
